{"tid":2438683,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有無人好僧万刀甲cctvb果D偽人? 不如like抵制tvb戰線page? Admin想搵返舊page戰友返黎","createTime":"2021-03-08T16:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T10:59:43.000Z","uid":364068,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8665ea306fbaae573f85d5df3a070569f71a24","tid":2438683,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqOxgXt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvqOxgXt.jpg&h=f4cc1110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=7ee3ea47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>差少少就5萬, 差幾萬就去返舊page8萬個數量 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實行<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">3萬THX</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !! <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />like返個page<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">= - = - =                         = - = - =                        = - = - =</p><br />\nCCTVB騎牆派食相難看極醜惡, <span class=\"limegreen\">連藍絲都話要抵制</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KBnujba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKBnujba.jpg&h=60e9803d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微博藍屍：黑醫護製造死亡病例抹黑祖國疫苗，TVB等毒媒如獲至寶<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2430146\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2430146</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">= - = - =                         = - = - =                        = - = - =</p><br />\n有鑑於派嬲人數下降，我哋係時候重新宣傳「抵制四部曲」，派嬲畀廣告商😡、留言解釋原因💬、互Like手足嘅留言👍🏻同埋分享貼文<br />\n-<br />\n以上行動喺呢年半以嚟，行之有效，連廣告界手足都認可，希望大家廣傳👍🏻<br />\n-<br />\n1️⃣【派嬲】<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">派嬲，係最直接對商家反映不滿嘅方式</span>，商家唔會知道我哋抵制文宣有幾多人睇過，佢哋只可以從派嬲人數參透一二，再推算喺TVB落廣告係咪真係會損害品牌形象，再者，俾其他顧客見到FB專頁咁多嬲嬲，觀感都唔好。<br />\n-<br />\n雖然，派嬲同留言都會推高廣告商貼文嘅觸及率，但係商家好怕醜聞，好想食盡兩家茶禮，而喺TVB落廣告某程度上就係一種醜聞，因為會得失黃營市場，你透過派嬲、留言方式推高對方嘅貼文觸及率，等於令全世界都知道對方係TVB廣告商，絕對係利多於弊。<br />\n-<br />\n2️⃣【留言】<br />\n留言，係要話畀商家、顧客聽點解要派嬲，亦係畀Marketers寫報告時作參考，以說服商家轉用其他宣傳渠道。<br />\n-<br />\n留言時包括以下幾個元素就最好，對方公司名、你抵制嘅原因、你會轉用邊間公司、醜聞（非必須），<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">但記住，唔好威脅／恐嚇對方。</span></span><br />\n-<br />\n3️⃣【互Like留言】<br />\n互Like手足嘅抵制留言，係為咗令佢出現喺貼文較高嘅位置，畀其他唔知情嘅顧客睇到。<br />\n-<br />\n另外，你哋亦可以派嬲畀其他顧客嘅留言，吸引對方嘅關注，再勸說對方轉用其他品牌。喺人哋個場，拉走人哋嘅客，不亦樂乎？<br />\n-<br />\n4️⃣【分享貼文】<br />\n為咗避免「同溫層效應」，我哋睇完貼文最好就Share埋出去，例如FB嘅十八區群組（可以大幅推高貼文觸及率）、屋企嘅Signal Group。<br />\n-<br />\n我哋嘅貼圖咁精美，你亦可以印製實體文宣，派畀朋友、同事或屋企人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mNV0qS4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNV0qS4.png&h=fc90a4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2eDWZS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2eDWZS.png&h=ba427b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQ9P3ES.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQ9P3ES.png&h=9f835d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Za0qTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Za0qTc.png&h=3f8dbe01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvQGUMx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvQGUMx.png&h=3b20735b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30eee1be462b1957b91cec38dcaa07c99779d6e0","tid":2438683,"uid":364068,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"re